	<a name="108113996053450145">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<a href="http://www.shirky.com/writings/situated_software.html">Shirky: Situated Software</a>.&nbsp; I may have blogged this earlier, but I am sure it wasn't the full article.&nbsp; Here is a lot more about situated software, and I think Clay relates it to another idea, one of small components, loosely held together (attributed to David Weinberger, I think).&nbsp; I like what is said here, though I can't say that I am working in that direction.&nbsp; So I need to see why not?<br>
